## New Project: tincture
- **Replaces:** tinycolor2 (8.9M weekly npm downloads, 4,086 dependents, 5.2K stars)
- **Why:** Abandoned 3+ years (last commit Feb 2023, 102 open issues). Primary fork @ctrl/tinycolor compromised in Shai-Hulud supply chain attack Sept 2025 (500+ packages infected, credential theft, CISA advisory). No safe maintained drop-in: colord abandoned (2022), chroma-js/colorjs.io have incompatible APIs.
- **Approach:** TypeScript-first, zero deps, ESM+CJS dual package. Full tinycolor2 API compat (~35 methods: parse/convert/modify/combine/readability). TinctureColor class with internal RGBA. Compat layer at tincture/compat/tinycolor2 for zero-change migration. OKLCH enhancement.
- **Package name:** tincture (verified available on npm)
- **GitHub repo:** agentine/tincture
- **Tasks assigned to project_manager:** #974 (Phase 1: core types/parsing/setup), #975 (Phase 2: conversion/properties), #976 (Phase 3: modification/combination/utilities), #977 (Phases 4-5: compat/testing/docs/release)

